body.description: Introducing our exquisite Durable and Recyclable Laundry Soap Dispenser. Crafted with precision and care, this dispenser offers a range of remarkable features that will elevate your laundry experience to new heights. DURABLE LAUNDRY DETERGENT LIQUID DISPENSER Embracing innovation, our dispenser is meticulously crafted from high-quality PET, BPA-free material. Unlike glass or metal alternatives, our dispenser is resilient to rust and breakage, ensuring its longevity. Plus,our laundry detergent storage container bundle includes a genuine bamboo tray. THOUGHTFUL PUMP DISPENSER DESIGN Say goodbye to messy spills and wasted detergent. Our dispenser boasts a lock-down pump mechanism, expertly engineered to prevent dripping and spilling. With this thoughtful feature, you can effortlessly dispense liquid without any unnecessary waste, ensuring every drop of your cherished laundry detergent or fabric softener counts. GENEROUS CAPACITY FABRIC SOFTENER DISPENSER Designed with your convenience in mind, our detergent dispenser flaunts an impressive 2000ml capacity. Bid farewell to frequent refills and embrace the luxury of ample storage.Not only will it enhance the aesthetics of your laundry area, but it will also ensure clarity and organization. LAUNDRY ROOM ORGANIZATION JARS Embrace versatility with our laundry soap dispenser. It effortlessly adapts to your ever-changing needs. Utilize it as a liquid laundry detergent dispenser, fabric softener dispenser, hand soap dispenser, dish soap dispenser, or even more. PACKAGE INCLUDES 2 x half gallon(2l) empty bottle. 1 x bamboo tray. 2 x pump heads. 1 x set of waterproof labels. 1 x collapsible silicone funnel. Indulge in the exquisite craftsmanship of our laundry containers for organizing. Uniting durability, functionality, and aesthetic appeal, this dispenser transcends the ordinary, bringing a touch of elegance to your laundry room. Experience the epitome of convenience, practicality, and style – a testament to our unwavering commitment to excellence.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on August 23, 2023
reviews.reviewText: One of the bottles arrived in with a dent at the top side but the dent would pop in and out. It was not cracked. The pumps are nice. It came with detergent and laundry sticker labels. I was hoping it came with shampoo and conditioner labels but did not. The bamboo tray is my favorite part of the set. Overall it’s a good product.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on January 18, 2024
reviews.reviewTitle: 4.0 out of 5 stars Great Products-Labels Useless
reviews.reviewText: I liked the tray, cup, funnel and bottles, they are half gallon bottles, smaller than I expected, but still a nice size. However, the labels they added were useless to me. I was looking for a bleach label and a sanitizer label. Or a blank one, and I can add sanitizer. But there were 3 detergent labels and 3 softener labels. That was disappointing, but not enough to return the whole set. I will probably just use my label maker to put over it but that's a hassle, I may just go with the detergent and softener labels.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on September 1, 2023
reviews.reviewText: These bottles work great. I like how they came with stickers for the bottles. They look really good in my laundry room.
